OL,5, A former lawyer for Baroness Mone has  
OL,6, apologised to the BBC for false        
OL,7, statements he made about money her     
OL,8, husband, Doug Barrowman, gave to the   
OL,9, Conservative Party.                    
OL,11,FLawyer Jonathan Coad told BBC News in  
OL,12,FDecember 2020 that Mr Barrowman had no 
OL,13,Fownership role with a firm that has    
OL,14,Fdonated more than #150,000 to the      
OL,15,FTories since 2017.                     
OL,17,FBut evidence has since emerged that    
OL,18,Fsuggests that was not the case.        
OL,20,FMr Barrowman has declined to comment.  
